should hostilities break out and go on for a while i see a 
scenario where people start saying consider a draft dicks said 
he said the country does not have a large enough volunteer force 
to support a prolonged military operation the call for a draft 
then would come from congress not the military dicks said 
mccain contended however that reactivation of the draft would 
be an indictment of the volunteer force 
if this crisis drives us back to reinstitution of the draft 
and this is a midsize crisis then an allvolunteer force will 
have been a failure he said 
