100 measures to protect canadas land water soil forests and 
wildlife over the next five years 
three billion dollars is a lot of money de cotret said at a 
news conference thats three thousand million dollars its all 
fresh new money the only thing recycled in the green plan is the 
paper its written on 
however opposition spokesmen and environmentalists criticized 
the plan calling it vague and lacking emphasis on enforcement of 
pollution regulations 
this document will do nothing to help the canadian 
