warming relations to upgrade the delegations in each others 
capitals 
during that period levin arrived in moscow and his delegation 
moved back into the building it occupied before ties were severed 
over the 1967 arabisraeli war 
despite the announcement the state of relations has not 
changed a soviet foreign ministry spokesman blamed slowmoving 
bureaucracy 
