1972 but this is the first time a target has been set the goal 
was set friday when reuss and march signed an agreement 
there is no doubt in my mind about the commitment of lloyd 
reuss and gm chairman bob stempel march said we are talking 
about a commitment from the largest corporation in the world 
in addition to adding to the minority dealer ratio a steering 
committee of the dealer organizations will look at ways to help 
dealers from minority groups stay in business 
blackowned innercity dealerships are especially vulnerable to 
economic downturns such as the one the auto industry currently is 
experiencing 
