the companys businesses that are not dependent on advertising such 
as professional infrmation book publishing and cable operations 
are showing healthy growth 
but he said the companys overall performance likely will 
continue to be weakened by the impact of the ad slump on the 
companys other businesses 
he did not provide specific earnings estimates and a 
spokeswoman said the company traditionally does not make such 
forecasts 
